					<h1><a href="http://www.makeurhealth.com/2010/11/26/benefits-of-drinking-water/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Benefits of Drinking Water!">Benefits of Drinking Water!</a></h1>

					<p class="postinfo">By <a href="http://www.makeurhealth.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> on Nov 26, 2010 in <a href="http://www.makeurhealth.com/category/health-articles/" title="View all posts in Health" rel="category tag">Health</a></p>
			
					<div class="entry">
<div align="left"><strong>Previous Post: </strong>&laquo; <a href="http://www.makeurhealth.com/2010/10/18/using-gadgets-to-treat-acid-reflux/" rel="prev">Using Gadgets to Treat Acid Reflux!</a></div>
<div align="right"><strong>Next Post:</strong><a href="http://www.makeurhealth.com/2010/12/13/pimples-on-face-causes-and-myths/" rel="next">Pimples on Face &#8211; causes and myths!</a> &raquo;</div><br \><br \>
<div style=”display:block;float:left;margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px;”>
<script type="text/javascript"><!--
google_ad_client = "ca-pub-5471401017301316";
/* MUH_Banner_Post */
google_ad_slot = "7243573551";
